    "updated_at": "2015-02-25T19:09:53Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The expected use of this is that there is only one set of rules per holiday class.  Namely there is a one-to-one mapping between holiday calendars and rules.  Ideally, if you change the rules you would create a new class.  However, this isn't exactly obvious from how things work and I don't see the harm in making the cache on the instance rather than the class (see #6719) for some design discussion.\n"
  },
